snippet.title: Five Night at Freddy's 2 - Subtitle Update on Mobile
snippet.description:
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/five-nights-at-freddys-2/id941143328

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.scottgames.fnaf2&hl=en_US&gl=US

It's a brand new restaurant! This time we have the latest animatronics with amazing safety features, Nothing can go wrong.....right?

Five Nights at Freddy's 2 is now updated to include subtitles for English, French, German, Dutch, Spanish (Latin America), Italian, Portuguese (Brazil), Russian, Japanese, Chinese (Simplified), Korean.

It's available now, If you speak one of these non-English languages please tell your friends to visit your favorite pizzeria! PLEASE NOTE: Fazbear Entertainment is not responsible for death or dismemberment.

Please follow our channel!

#MadeWithFusion #FNaF
